high_descs: Walk straight, turn right to face the drawer, walk straight to the drawer.
Pick up the pen on top of the drawer.
Turn around to face the bed, walk straight to the sofa seat, turn right when you reach the sofa seat and walk straight to the small table.
Place the pen on top of the small table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pen on top of a small table.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk up to the dresser.
Pick up the pen off of the top of the dresser.
Turn around and walk to the other side of the room, making a right when you reach the chair, then walk until you make it to the bedside table.
Place the pen onto the round bedside table, next to the credit card.
anns.task_desc: Grab a pen off of the dresser and place it on the bedside table.

high_descs: Turn right and cross the room to the white desk.
Pick up the black pen to the right of the silver plant vase.
Turn around, cross to the black chair, hang a right to the brown woven basket and turn right to face the small table.
Place the pen on the table in front of the red card closest to you.
anns.task_desc: Place a pen on a small table.
